---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Missable Achievements Guide"
  description="Complete guide to all missable achievements in Hollow Knight: Silksong. Critical timing and requirements to avoid missing permanently lost achievements."
  keywords="missable achievements, pharloom's welcome, twisted child, lace boss, grand mother silk, critical achievements"
>
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
          <span class="text-red-400 font-medium">Critical Warning</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
          <span class="gradient-text">Missable Achievements Guide</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          Essential guide to achievements that can be permanently missed if not completed at the right time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Critical Warning -->
      <div class="bg-red-900/20 border border-red-400/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <span class="text-white text-sm font-bold">!</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-400 mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              These achievements <strong>cannot be obtained</strong> if you progress too far in the story without completing them first.
              Make sure to complete them as soon as the opportunities become available.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Missable Achievements List -->
      <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">

        <!-- Pharloom's Welcome -->
        <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6 border border-red-500/30">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-400">Pharloom's Welcome</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">MOST CRITICAL - Early Game</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Missable Window</div>
              <div class="text-red-400 font-semibold">Act 1 Only</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-900/20 rounded p-4 mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">Critical Requirement</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
              Defeat Lace in Deep Docks <strong>before advancing to Act 2</strong>. Once you progress the main story,
              Lace will no longer be available for this fight.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-silksong-blue">How to Complete</h4>
              <ol class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <li>1. Reach Deep Docks area</li>
                <li>2. Find Lace near the underwater ruins</li>
                <li>3. Defeat her in combat</li>
                <li>4. Achievement unlocks immediately</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-red-400">Deadline</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Must complete before story progression</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Before entering Citadel Upper District</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Before meeting the Weavers</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ NO second chance available</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded p-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
              <strong>Tip:</strong> Make this your top priority when you first reach Deep Docks. Don't explore other areas first.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Twisted Child -->
        <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6 border border-red-500/30">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">üï∑Ô∏è</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-400">Twisted Child</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">CRITICAL - Mid Game</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Missable Window</div>
              <div class="text-red-400 font-semibold">Before Silk Road</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-900/20 rounded p-4 mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">Multi-Step Process</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
              Must obtain curse from Greyroot in Shellwood, then defeat Grand Mother Silk while cursed.
              Both the curse and boss fight have limited availability windows.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-silksong-blue">Step-by-Step</h4>
              <ol class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <li>1. Reach Shellwood area</li>
                <li>2. Find Greyroot NPC</li>
                <li>3. Accept the curse (temporary debuff)</li>
                <li>4. Travel to Grand Mother Silk boss</li>
                <li>5. Defeat her while still cursed</li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-red-400">Curse Effects</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <li>‚Ä¢ 25% less maximum health</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ 15% slower movement</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Darker screen filter</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Lasts 30 minutes real-time</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded p-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
              <strong>Warning:</strong> The curse wears off over time. You must defeat the boss before it expires.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Steel Soul Warrior -->
        <div class="bg-silksong-dark rounded-lg p-6 border border-yellow-500/30">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-white text-xl">‚öîÔ∏è</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-400">Steel Soul Warrior</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">EXTREME - Permadeath Mode</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Difficulty</div>
              <div class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold">Extreme</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-yellow-900/20 rounded p-4 mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-2">Steel Soul Mode</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
              Complete the entire game without dying even once. Death immediately ends the run and
              forces you to start over from the beginning.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-silksong-blue">Strategy Tips</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Over-prepare for every encounter</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Learn all boss patterns first</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Use the strongest build possible</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Take your time, avoid risky shortcuts</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-yellow-400">Essential Tools</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Pin Badge for faster kills</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Quick Focus for safe healing</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Strength for higher damage</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ All mask shards collected</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-silksong-darker rounded p-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
              <strong>Note:</strong> This is technically missable because it requires a fresh save file. If you die once, you must restart completely.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Prevention Checklist -->
      <div class="bg-silksong-dark/50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-silksong-gold">Prevention Checklist</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-silksong-blue">Before Act 2</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" class="mr-2" id="lace-fight">
                <label for="lace-fight">Complete Lace fight in Deep Docks</label>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" class="mr-2" id="early-exploration">
                <label for="early-exploration">Explore all accessible areas thoroughly</label>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" class="mr-2" id="tool-collection">
                <label for="tool-collection">Collect essential tools first</label>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-silksong-purple">Mid Game</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" class="mr-2" id="greyroot-curse">
                <label for="greyroot-curse">Get curse from Greyroot</label>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" class="mr-2" id="silk-boss">
                <label for="silk-boss">Defeat Grand Mother Silk while cursed</label>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <input type="checkbox" class="mr-2" id="steel-soul-prep">
                <label for="steel-soul-prep">Plan Steel Soul run early</label>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-between">
        <a href="/guides" class="btn-secondary text-center">
          ‚Üê Back to All Guides
        </a>
        <a href="/achievements" class="btn-primary text-center">
          View All Achievements ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A90E2 0%, #7B68EE 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
</style>